trans-unit.source: Defines methods for reading the parts of a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
Gets a collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> readers for each document in a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션을 가져옵니다 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> 각 문서에 대 한 판독기는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: A collection of <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> readers, one for each document in a <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 컬렉션 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> 독자에 있는 각 문서에 대 한 한 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reader for the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> with the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 판독기를 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> 지정 된 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-uri-md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets a reader for the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref> with the specified [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](../Token/TLA%23tla_uri_md.md)].
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 판독기를 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"> </xref> 지정 된 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_uri](../Token/TLA%23tla_uri_md.md)]합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref>, if one exists, that is associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocument"></xref>.

For more information about the <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket> part of an [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] sequence, see chapter 2 in the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] specification, which you can obtain at [XPS: Specification and License Downloads](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).
trans-unit.target: 에 대 한 자세한 내용은 <xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>의 일부가 [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_xps](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-xps-md.md)] 시퀀스, 2 장 참조는 [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xps](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] 사양에서 가져올 수 있습니다 [XPS: 사양 및 라이선스 다운로드](http://www.microsoft.com/whdc/xps/downloads.mspx).</xref:System.Printing.PrintTicket>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"></xref> that contains the default printing options for the sequence; or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>, if no print ticket exists for the document.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Printing.PrintTicket"> </xref> 시퀀스에 대 한 기본 인쇄 옵션을 포함 하는 또는 <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>없는 인쇄 티켓 문서에 있는 경우.

trans-unit.source: Gets the thumbnail image, if one exists, that is associated with the <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: 연결 된 있는 경우 미리 보기 이미지를 가져옵니다는 <xref href="System.Windows.Documents.FixedDocumentSequence"> </xref>합니다.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Uri> that represents the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] for the sequence.
